{"tid":1592644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愈叫唔好愈想做","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:59:24.000Z","uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b1359078ad113b707eb60750549d892557115de8","tid":1592644,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />owhowuouoeueoheoow!!!!<br />\noeeuwupiolsiokoejodwueoeouj oiowuwjjw<br />\noyouheowjiwhheojeihej<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f28af896091c94a5272d7d0403ca82daac8c0b","tid":1592644,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"做lo"},{"pid":"4a7ab8ee7d647b140dc3943bcf82c064fdbb2cdf","tid":1592644,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=567b29a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTs8Wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTs8Wx.jpg&h=306d0b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;關於Logo投票&gt;</span></span><br />\nHK Assembly成立的目的，不單是讓全港市民議論政事，更希望建立民主平台，讓全民以公投方式發聲，同時將平台民主制度完善，成為能與政制競爭的類政制。<br />\n但是在達到理想前，必須逐步累積技術和經驗。因此，我們決定對投票機制進行第一次測試，以現階段盡量民主的方式讓大家選出共同的「香港全民議政會」Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;投票機制&gt;</span></span><br />\n投票採用兩輪的簡單多數制。最高票數的兩款將交由設計師作最後加工，在第二輛投票獲較高票數的一款將成為 HK Assembly 的官方 Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">規則：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">一人一票</span> [1] <br />\n2. 第一輪投票時間：<span style=\"color: violet;\">24/9 11PM - 26/9 11PM</span> （香港時間，共48小時）[2]<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=567b29a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票需要你：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">加入Channel：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=567b29a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">投票</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">叫朋友</span>加入Channel一起投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;感謝支持&gt;</span></span><br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人<span style=\"color: violet;\">致謝</span>。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立<span style=\"color: violet;\">真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台</span>。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">投票救港</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=567b29a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3]<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】</span></span>隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"df5f554bf1912430d4a1fb0dbb00e881ebcfcf85","tid":1592644,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"b2df1c64f13253ce4f08ed6121fed033a32aae19","tid":1592644,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086f7cbc2cecfc126174de89b6feea322196b865","tid":1592644,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊"},{"pid":"1a8ae15c4dc0c6be6c5bbb02388e00524a33b876","tid":1592644,"uid":251643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"7811ad170db1ff1dfb234840eaf67588d06292e0","tid":1592644,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"開膠post 俾人屌<br />\n想轉場去鄉土玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cb48f98b625a62be808a280ef36f6322ac783d","tid":1592644,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1359078ad113b707eb60750549d892557115de8","tid":1592644,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:29.